=====================================================================
|ID|OPERATOR                         |NAME    |EST.ROWS|EST.TIME(us)|
---------------------------------------------------------------------
|0 |NESTED-LOOP OUTER JOIN CARTESIAN |        |1       |402         |
|1 |├─SUBPLAN SCAN                   |t_all   |1       |1           |
|2 |│ └─EXPRESSION                   |        |1       |1           |
|3 |└─PX COORDINATOR                 |        |1       |4           |
|4 |  └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR           |:EX10000|1       |3           |
|5 |    └─PX BLOCK ITERATOR          |        |1       |3           |
|6 |      └─TABLE GET                |t1      |1       |3           |
=====================================================================
